Guild Type: Club
Name: Beggars Club of Kabal
Members: Anyone below 50 average stats that are within -500 to 500
         in allignment and has done a small quest (beggarsclubquest).
         Only restrictions on joining, none later.

- This club is a byproduct of the Kabal life of trading and merchant-life.
   Here the lowest of people, beggars, has made themselves a small club
   where they can unite in skills (emotes in the club) in how to beg better.
   Since this club is based on helping the members to beg, no utter evil or
   good prsons may join, and they cannot be of a high level of experience.
   Its a place for the msmall and poor ones.

- Benefits from joining :

   Role-playing opportunities ...
   Giving the small players emotes for the usual -got any cash?-
   Fun, and a mirrorimage for the richmansclub. Balances it iup :)
   Can buy a robe that has some more emotes in it (ac 1)
- Disatvantages :
   
   None really.

The club can be found in /d/Kalad/common/central/circle/beggar_hut.c
Creator : korat.
